              <span class="font-bold text-[var(--color-gold)]">$2,000-3,000</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
            Entry-level SLA printer with dedicated 3D editing Mac for creating burnout patterns. Perfect for small to medium jewelry pieces with high precision and smooth surfaces.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 2: Professional Studio -->
        <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg p-6">
