            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-neutral-600">Multiple Resin Types:</span>
              <span class="font-semibold">$500-1,000</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-neutral-600">Advanced Accessories:</span>
              <span class="font-semibold">$1,000-2,000</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-neutral-600">Studio Setup:</span>
              <span class="font-semibold">$2,000-3,000</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between border-t pt-2">
              <span class="text-neutral-900 font-semibold">Total Phase 2:</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-[var(--color-gold)]">$10,000-15,000</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
            Professional studio setup with multiple printers, high-end 3D editing workstation, advanced materials, and dedicated workspace for high-volume production.
          </p>
        </div>
